item.title: Cool Pets NFT
item.description: An NFT offering from the Cool Cats brand, Pets is a collection of 19,999 NFTs that are procedurally generated based on item interaction. All Pets start as an Egg and evolve into their final form, which represents one of four elements: Grass, Fire, Water, or Air. Users can evolve their Pet through our gamified experience on coolcatsnft –your final Pet is one of 17 million possible outcomes! We love the Pets!
